  "keyFeatures": [
    "Nix Flakes with blueprint framework for organized multi-host management",
    "Catppuccin Mocha theming system-wide via Stylix",
    "Secret management with agenix (age-encrypted secrets)",
    "ZFS filesystem with automatic snapshots and scrubbing",
    "Self-hosted services: GoToSocial, Matrix (tuwunel), Home Assistant, Gonic, Copyparty, Etherpad",
    "Tailscale VPN with SSH access across all hosts",
    "GNOME desktop with declarative dconf settings and locked configuration",
    "WSL support for Windows development environments",
    "Cloudflare Tunnel for secure service exposure",
    "Home Manager for per-user dotfile and application management"
  ],
